Novartis Lowers Price for Lucentis Drug By 30 Percent, AWP Says

-- B y   C o r i n n e   G r e t l e r
-- 
2011-10-05T16:19:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/novartis-lowers-price-for-lucentis-drug-by-30-percent-awp-says.html
Novartis AG (NOVN)  will lower the price of
its Lucentis drug by 30 percent following pressure from Swiss
authorities, Swiss news agency AWP said, citing Le Matin
newspaper.  The reduction will also affect prices outside  Switzerland 
as they are derived from prices in the country, AWP said, citing
